description:
budgie-desktop supports IBus - as you can see we also support Fcitx as well.  We just need to make the switch from IBus to Fcitx (and back) as easy as possible.  This is just one of the many interesting issues we need to resolve.

Have you ever contributed a bit of code to an open-source project?

Here is your chance - this and many other interesting issues await for anyone with any of the following skills python/HTML/CSS/Javascript -

Pop over to our chat room to discuss (https://gitter.im/budgie-remix/community) - or have a look through the issues (https://github.com/budgie-remix/budgie-welcome/issues) and help-out!
